additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Water, Soybeans, Rice, Salt, Alcohol. Contains 3.34mL/100g alcohol. Alcohol will be reduced after cooking. Natural colour may darken but this will not affect the taste or quality.

additionalProperty.name: Country Of Origin
additionalProperty.value: Made in Japan from Imported ingredients

description: Originated from Japan, Hikari Miso Shinshu Aka Miso (Red) offers an authentic miso that is only made with water, soybeans, rice, salt and alcohol. It has a deep umami taste that is perfect for soups and braises.
name: Red Miso Paste
